&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/USA-HONOLULU-CHEF-MAVRO-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7425&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/USA-HONOLULU-CHEF-MAVRO-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- HONOLULU- CHEF MAVRO- OFFER- LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;For over 25 years Chef George Mavrothalassitis has been at the forefront of Hawaii Regional Cuisine sourcing from local farmers and fishermen. As chef/proprietor of Honolulu&rsquo;s Chef Mavro restaurant he won the prestigious James Beard award, considered the &ldquo;Oscars&rdquo; of the culinary world. Chef Mavro is the only independently owned restaurant in Hawaii to hold the American Automobile Association (AAA) Five Diamond award and also the highest food rating in Hawaii, 18/20 Gayot as well as a coveted place on their &ldquo;Top 40 Restaurants in the U.S.&rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A modern chef using classic French techniques, Chef Mavro features the very best products from Hawaii and around the world in his flexible 4- and 6-course menus as well as the Grand Degustation- an&nbsp;11 course dinner&nbsp;plus amuse bouche and pre-dessert with&nbsp;a personalized menu.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Also known for wine pairings, a committee carefully selects wine pairings when new recipes are created each season. The dining room has a welcoming, relaxed elegance with warm and gracious service. &nbsp;The restaurant is just 5 minutes from Waikiki. Evening resort attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at &lt;a title=&quot;Chef Mavro&quot; href=&quot;http://www.chefmavro.com/reservations&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;Chef Mavro&amp;#8217;s website&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;or contact Chef Mavro by phone at +1-808-944-4714 or email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:chef@chefmavro.com&quot;&gt;chef@chefmavro.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Chef Mavro offers only course dining with a choice of flexible 4- and 6-course menus and a Grand Degustation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must use your Diners Club card for payment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

